Rating: 4
Just made this wonderfully creamy cheesecake with a few changes. I added 1Tbl Limoncello (a lemon liquor from Italy) to the batter. I had some fresh cherries so I pitted them, cut them in half and soaked them in some more Limoncello for about 1/2 hour. I usually go for the heavier cheesecakes, but this was wonderful!!!!

